  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps 24</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Les Dolomites is a spacious chalet located on the main street running into the centre of Val d’Isère. This property was also renovated in 2013 with new bedrooms and en suite bathrooms throughout. The Solaise Express ski lift is a short bus ride away (or a 10 minute walk), providing easy access to the slopes and ski school. In the evenings, the free bus service runs until 2:30am in high season, for those wishing to make the most of this resort’s notorious nightlife.</p>
<p>There are four bedrooms on each floor, all with en suite shower rooms and three out of the four with a balcony. The bedrooms are a good size and very comfortable. Rooms 1, 5 and 9 can take an extra put up bed for children when the chalet is taken exclusively.</p>]]></description>
